     <tr><td>
          <table width="100%"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
            <tr>
              <td class="main">Where do we start? Stability, security, no more malicious spyware installing itself on your computer and wreaking havoc. There are so many reasons it's hard to decide. Most importantly, Ubuntu provides you with the freedom to use the software you like, the way you like to use it. You are not locked into any formats that are controlled by large corporations. You choose. Ubuntu also has legendary stability. No more blue screens of death when you boot up. Ubuntu is also easy to use. The learning curve is short and worth while. Once you move, you'll never look back. <br><br><hr class="rule-mainpage">
